data.description: Located in the serene Senior Community of Camarillo Springs, this lovely home is move-in ready for you! You are welcomed into a spacious and cozy living room as you step through the front door. The beautiful vaulted ceilings are reminiscent of a mountain cabin. This well-cared for home was built in 2000, featuring an open concept living space and three generously sized bedrooms! The master en-suite includes a walk-in closet with ample shelving space. With an abundance of windows, the home is light and bright all year round. Great location just a walk away from the clubhouse and pool. Easy freeway access too! Call for your private showing today!
